C помошью методы .createNewFile()

Тестирующий код:

public class KataClass {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        File file = new File("C:\\Users\\User\\Desktop\\KataDirectory\\file.txt");
        
        try {
            file.createNewFile();
        } catch (IOException e) {
            System.out.println("Something went wrong");
            e.printStackTrace();
        }
    }
}
